data.description: **NO HOA** 5 Garage Doors = 5+ Garage Kept Vehicles. 2 Car Attached Garage, DETACHED GARAGE that features 3 GARAGE Doors, Heat, A/C, Fans and enough parking for 4 cars or use one bay to keep that RV out of the winter/summer elements. Situated on 5.25 Acres in Southern Maryland, this Flag Lot PRIVATE OASIS provides plenty of yard space, beautiful trees, creek that runs along the property, all for Private Enjoyment.  Stunning CUSTOM CAPE COD home on the private street of Pasture Place. Watch all the wildlife, deer, turtles, etc right from your back deck. Walking into this home you're greeted with wood Cathedral Ceilings over an Open Concept Kitchen with Granite counters overlooking the living room, and formal dining area. The living room showcases a beautiful stone fireplace and wall to wall windows and doors that lead to the back deck and beautiful backyard. The lot also features a creek that runs along the acreage tucked in the trees on the outer edges of the lot. Besides the Bonus area in the upstairs area of the detached garage can be used for storage or finish off for a future bonus suite. Need that Fenced in Doggie area that doesn’t impact the entertaining portion of the yard, fully fenced in Doggie Park right there in your own backyard. Do you want to host your own cornhole tournaments, or build a personal pickleball court, and walk right into your basement already set up for pool, darts, gaming, drinks bar, workout space, and semi finished half bath. Over 1800 sq ft of FINISHED BASEMENT that can be quickly converted to an apartment for in-laws or those older college kids.  *****MAIN BEDROOM /BATHROOM ON THE FIRST FLOOR ***** with Walk In Closet and Sliders that lead on the back deck where you can sit and enjoy nature and your morning coffee. And,.....MAIN BEDROOM/BATHROOM/IN-LAW SUITE ON SECOND FLOOR. Only 30 miles to Patuxent River Naval Base, 31 miles to Joint Base Andrews, and 42 miles to Naval Academy in Annapolis. Close proximity to local park, boat launch, fishing pier, shops, grocery store, only 3 miles to local VINEYARD, restaurants and more. (Basement Sauna does not convey, along with some other specific items) ***MOST OF THE HOUSE AND BASEMENT FURNITURE FOR ENTERTAINING CONVEYS WITH HOME IF YOUR BUYERS WOULD LIKE TO HAVE A HOME THAT IS MOSTLY FURNISHED***"HOME COMES WITH JOHN DEER TRACTOR WITH BLOWER AND PLOW ATTACHMENT***  AGENTS***** Sellers had investigations completed on the gasoline tank. See disclosures. Some lenders may require this report.
